    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": null,
      "speakerName": "",
      "iconUrl": null,
      "voiceUrl": null,
      "text": "――ある日の打ち合わせにて",
      "startTime": 0,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei001.m4a",
      "text": "えー！？　芽衣がもし恋のヒロインに選ばれたの！？\n怜ちゃんと渚ちゃんが出てたやつだよね！？",
      "startTime": 6.8333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "ああ。夏休み前の忙しいところ申し訳ないが\nぜひ芽衣に協力してほしいとのことだ",
      "startTime": 14.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei002.m4a",
      "text": "楽しそう！　芽衣にやらせて！\nあのゲームのヒロインになれるなんて嬉しいな～",
      "startTime": 20.5333333333,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei003.m4a",
      "text": "芽衣も怜ちゃんみたいに、最初は冷たいけど\n実は優しい子っていう設定だったりして",
      "startTime": 28.8999988556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei004.m4a",
      "text": "渚ちゃんみたいな、幼なじみっていう設定もいいよね\n朝から家に「おはよー」って起こしに行くの！",
      "startTime": 37.2999988556,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei005.m4a",
      "text": "ねえねえ、{user}さん！\n芽衣のお話はどんな感じになるの？",
      "startTime": 43.2999988556,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_paper-01.m4a",
          "delay": 6610.001144399995,
          "startTime": 49.91
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "そのことなんだが\nまずはこの書類に目を通してほしいんだ",
      "startTime": 48.4666655223,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei006.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、これはアンケート？\n恋愛観に、好きなシチュエーション……",
      "startTime": 57.2333321889,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "mei",
      "speakerName": "早坂芽衣",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-mei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01_short/sud_vo_adv_card_mei_09_01-mei007.m4a",
      "text": "理想のデートに、告白について……",
      "startTime": 62.1083215951,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}